{{about|the economist|the theologian|Albrecht Ritschl (theologian)}}

'''Albrecht Ritschl''' is Professor of [[Economic History]] at the [[London School of Economics]].<ref>[http://personal.lse.ac.uk/ritschl/ Albrecht Ritschl]</ref> He studied at the [[University of Munich]], and previously taught at the [[Pompeu Fabra University]], the [[University of Zurich]] and the [[Humboldt University of Berlin]].<ref>[http://personal.lse.ac.uk/ritschl/al_cv.html Albrecht Ritschl - CV]</ref>

